msgid "# Supported Features"
msgstr "# 支持的功能"

msgid ""
"The feature support principle of vLLM Ascend is: **aligned with vLLM**. We "
"are also actively collaborating with the community to accelerate support."
msgstr "vLLM Ascend 的功能支持原则是：**与 vLLM 保持一致**。我们也在积极与社区合作，加速支持。"

msgid ""
"Functional call: <https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/features/tool_calling/>"
msgstr "功能调用：<https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/features/tool_calling/>"

msgid ""
"You can check the [support status of vLLM V1 Engine][v1_user_guide]. Below "
"is the feature support status of vLLM Ascend:"
msgstr "您可以查看 [vLLM V1 引擎的支持状态][v1_user_guide]。以下是 vLLM Ascend 的功能支持状态："

msgid ""
"- 🟢 Functional: Fully operational, with ongoing optimizations.\n"
"- 🔵 Experimental: Experimental support, interfaces and functions may change.\n"
"- 🚧 WIP: Under active development, will be supported soon.\n"
"- 🟡 Planned: Scheduled for future implementation (some may have open PRs/RFCs).\n"
"- 🔴 NO plan/Deprecated: No plan or deprecated by vLLM."
msgstr ""
"- 🟢 功能完备：完全可用，持续优化中。\n"
"- 🔵 实验性：实验性支持，接口和功能可能发生变化。\n"
"- 🚧 开发中：正在积极开发，即将支持。\n"
"- 🟡 已计划：计划在未来实现（部分可能有开放的 PR/RFC）。\n"
"- 🔴 无计划/已弃用：无计划或已被 vLLM 弃用。"

